overview: Alecia Fox is a curious student always willing to explore and discover new things and soon she will discover all the mischief and sex that occurs at Private school… Going to the library to get a book? Tiffany Tatum’s already there with the gym teacher and they’re not exactly reading. A nice walk in the garden? Veronica Leal’s got that covered enjoying more than just the sun with her man. And that’s just the beginning… join Alecia as she discovers a school full of horny students and teachers as Cherry Kiss seduces her two professors into a threesome and Anny Aurora gets down and dirty with the headmaster. And what for Alecia? Find out right here in Private Gold/College Harlots- Back to School, the ultimate teen experience!
title: College Harlots - Back To School
